104
00:11:04,831 --> 00:11:07,706
I'm even afraid
to sit at a desk.

105
00:11:07,708 --> 00:11:09,876
Well, write outside, then.

106
00:11:09,878 --> 00:11:12,420
A lot of people come
here to work...

107
00:11:12,422 --> 00:11:15,716
