gets bashed against a boulder.

233
00:22:22,675 --> 00:22:24,257
Right.

234
00:22:24,259 --> 00:22:25,426
No, if we don't see
Seventh Seal,

235
00:22:25,428 --> 00:22:26,885
then at least a nice one.

